This is a example project to implement the queue message broker rabbitMQ on a simil real scenario.

Architecture diagram.


There are 3 services on the project

BACKEND.
This services simulates some kind on api request from a new post user.
First the service saves on a sqlite db the new item post
After tries to connect to a rabbitmq service and send a message with data from the new post 

EMAIL 
This service connect to a rabbitMQ service, gets all messages from the backend service and send a email to a user

IMAGE 
This service connect to a rabbitMQ service gets all messages from the backend service and generate a new thumbnail image 
from a new item post.






